Kang Hyung-gu (Korean: 강형구; born (1998-01-27)January 27, 1998), better known as Kino (키노), is a South Korean singer, songwriter, rapper, composer and dancer.
He is best known as the member of the boy group Pentagon, which debuted in 2016 under Cube Entertainment.
I wanted to find a name that could show myself as a singer and in the team in the future, so Kino became it.
